<h3 class="gcf-ttl-h3">■改修前後のワイン城の対比（左：改修前 右：改修後イメージ）</h3>
<figure class="lyt-image">
<img src="https://img.furusato-tax.jp/img/x/gcf/project/form/details/20181025/gpfd_3aff3db9ec6d8e8c01bf7077556cc57afa831240.png" />
